# CELIA-012 - Add Transaction

## Epic

Transactions

## Goal

Allow users to create new transactions.

## User Story

As a user,
I want to record income and expenses
so that I can track my finances.

## Scope

Implement the Add Transaction modal.

Fields:

- Date
- Member
- Income / Expense
- Bucket
- Subcategory
- Amount
- Notes
- Recurring toggle

Persist the transaction.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] Transaction modal implemented
- [ ] Validation for required fields
- [ ] Transaction saved
- [ ] Persistence verified
- [ ] Transaction appears in list
- [ ] Tests added
- [ ] Verification pipeline passes

## Dependencies

- CELIA-011

## Out of Scope

- Editing
- Spreadsheet